	<h3 class="LeafTitle" id="LeafTitle">
		Current Jobs
	</h3><div class="LeafContent" id="LeafContent">
		<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); "><span style="font-size: x-large; "><font face="Arial, serif"><b>Senior Application Developer</b></font></span></span></p>
<p class="western"><span style="font-size: medium; "><font face="Arial, serif"><b>Position Summary:</b></font></span><font color="#222222"><font face="Arial, serif"><font size="2"><b> </b></font></font></font></p>
<p>VertaSource is seeking a hard working, motivated and talented developer to join a fast paced, cutting edge team to help build large scale web applications.  We work in a full stack environment to build cutting edge web applications.</p>
<h3>Required Skills / Qualifications:</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Ability to work independently and efficiently to meet deadlines</li>
    <li>Proficiency in developing full stack applications</li>
    <li>Minimum of 4 years of software development experience</li>
    <li>Strong background in C#, ASP.NET or similar technologies</li>
    <li>Experience with a javascript framework: Angular, Knockout, Backbone, Ember, etc</li>
    <li>Proficiency with jQuery or Mootools</li>
    <li>Knowledge of SQL, Mongodb, JavaScript, Design Patterns and RESTful Web Services</li>
    <li>Experience in server side MVC frameworks</li>
</ul>
<h3>Responsibilities:</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Work with a team to develop high end web applications.</li>
    <li>Assist in the development of new processes as necessary to ensure mission critical systems are completed.</li>
    <li>Ensure team compliance with standards and procedures. Recognize code, process and/or standard inefficiencies and suggest new standards and opportunities for improvement</li>
    <li>Analysis of system requirements to determine feasibility of design within time and cost constraints</li>
    <li>Maintenance and upkeep of existing and legacy systems</li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 102, 255);"><strong>How To Apply:</strong></span><br />
Please apply by submitting via email to jobs@vertasource.com or by mailing to:<br />
VertaSource <br />
Attention: Human Resources<br />
403 Main Street, Suite 250<br />
Buffalo NY 14203</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>Equal Opportunity Employer –M/F/D/V</strong></span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family: Arial, serif; font-size: x-large;">Account Executive</b></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">VertaSource is seeking an Account Executive to help grow our business. The Account Executive position will contribute to VertaSource’s success by aligning customer needs with VertaSource competencies and grow revenue.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">The desired candidate should have experience in selling online application solutions to meet clients’ business objectives. Additionally the potential candidate should be able to demonstrate historical sales success for a consecutive 3 year period.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">A potential candidate should possess the following characteristics:</span></span></p>
<ul>
    <li><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">Be a motivated self-starter who needs little direction.</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">Have strong interpersonal skills both verbal and written.</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">Have experience with a solutions selling process.</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">Have strong proposal writing skills.</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">Be comfortable selling an intangible services product.</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">Understand and follow a formal sales process with CRM reporting.</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">Be able to assess opportunities to align with company goals.</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">Job responsibilities to include:</span></span></p>
<ul>
    <li><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">Cold call to “C” level executives.</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">Manage an active sales funnel with multiple opportunities at various sales stages.</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">Meet monthly sales objectives for each level of the sales process.</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">Maintain client relationships with the project team.</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">Become a valued team member.</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">Compensation is salary and commission commensurate with experience.</span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: small;">Interested candidates should forward their resume to Jobs@VertaSource.com. </span></span></p>
	</div>
